### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@todoId = 1

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### GET - Listar todos
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos

### GET - Listar con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos?completed=false&priority=high&sort=priority

### GET - Obtener uno
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/{{todoId}}

### POST - Crear
POST {{baseUrl}}/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Nueva tarea",
  "description": "Descripción",
  "priority": "high"
}

### PUT - Actualizar
PUT {{baseUrl}}/todos/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Actualizado",
  "completed": true,
  "priority": "medium"
}

### PATCH.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/todos/1/toggle

### DELETE - Eliminar
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/todos/5

### Error: Título muy corto
POST {{baseUrl}}/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hey"
}

### ID INVÁLIDO.
GET {{baseUrl}}/todos/abc
